.TH wxGridCellRenderer 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxGridCellRenderer \- This class is responsible for actually drawing the cell in the grid.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
You may pass it to the \fIwxGridCellAttr\fR (below) to change the format of one given cell or to \fIwxGrid:setDefaultRenderer/2\fR to change the view of all cells. This is an abstract class, and you will normally use one of the predefined derived classes or derive your own class from it.

.PP
